git note for adding others' repo into mime:
 * add submodule:
    $ git submodule add <FULL GIT REPO PATH> <local folder name>
    $ git submodule update --init
    $ cd <local folder name>
    $ git pull origin master
    $ cd ..
    $ git commit -m'add a new submodule'


